5 1 This Act may be cited as the Nature Conservancy Council Act 1973. 2 The enactments specified in Schedule 4 to this Act are hereby repealed to the extent mentioned in column 3 of that Schedule. 3 . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .  this Act does not extend to Northern Ireland.
